RATIONALE FOR APACHE-2.0

This package contains shared utilities, cryptographic functions, and
common data structures used across the Birthmark ecosystem. We use
Apache-2.0 to enable broad reuse without licensing restrictions.

These utilities may be incorporated into both open-source and
proprietary implementations of Birthmark-compatible systems.
